### Decision: Phase 1.1 (Config & Persistence) complete for cowork-orchestrator:

1. src/config/schema.ts — Zod v4

**Date:** 2026-02-17
**Context:** Phase 1
**Decision:** Phase 1.1 (Config & Persistence) complete for cowork-orchestrator:

1. src/config/schema.ts — Zod v4 schemas validating OrchestratorConfig with defaults (maxConcurrentAgents:10, maxConcurrentTasks:50, defaultTimeout:300000, checkpointInterval:30000, rateLimits:{rpm:60,tpm:100000}, persistence:{enabled:true, dbPath:'./data/orchestrator.db'}). Exports DEFAULT_CONFIG and validateConfig().

2. src/config/defaults.ts — Re-exports DEFAULT_CONFIG and validateConfig from schema.ts.

3. src/memory/persistence.ts — PersistenceLayer class using better-sqlite3 with WAL mode. Tables: tasks, agents, messages, checkpoints, audit_log (with indexes). Full CRUD for tasks/agents/messages, saveCheckpoint/getLatestCheckpoint, appendAuditLog/queryAuditLog. Custom PersistenceError class. AuditEntry.workflowId stored in data JSON column. All methods wrapped in try/catch. Compiles cleanly with tsc --noEmit.
**Reasoning:** 

